Subject: 2 Chatham Road West Ryde - CC Kick off Meeting
 
Good Afternoon All,
 
On behalf of Ventus, I would like to welcome engaged consultants as part of the design team to deliver the CC for the project at 2 Chatham Road West Ryde NSW 2114.
 
The consultants list of the project is attached for your reference, and the main point of contact for this project will be myself. Please CC the relevant consultants in all correspondences where necessary.
 

Project Information:

    NCC 2022
    Building incorporates Classes 2, 6 and 7
    CC staging as follows:
        PTC     Demolition and remediation (demolition and remediation that does not involve building works does not require a CC)
        CC1      Piling, shoring, anchoring, excavation, capping beam, stormwater tap in, sewer tap in, undergrounding of services 
        CC2      Structure up to roof and required BCA E1D16 fire services
        CC3      Remainder of works – Architecture, façade services, landscaping
    Note: S4.55 will be submitted with the scope of a revised façade design to minimise the number of aluminium feature blades.
    https://app.procore.com/2483653/project/specification_sections
 
 

Initial Coordination Meeting:

    Our first design meeting will be on Tuesday 24th October 2023 @ 10.30am. The meeting will be held in person at Shop 4, 30-32 Herbert Street West Ryde NSW 2114.
    Meeting Agenda attached and relevant documents are within that document.
    Required consultants for the first design meeting in person:
        Architect – MX Designs
        Structural – HHC Engineers
        Stormwater – SGC
        Civil – Xavier Knight
        BCA – Jensen Hughes
        Hydraulic/Fire – Scott Collis Consulting
        Mechanical – Premium Consulting Engineers
        Electrical – Tricom Engineering Group
        The remaining consultants are free to join on teams.
    All DA documents, stamped plans, etc are in Procore and the attached – to be reviewed ahead of the meeting.
    Please review the attached DA matrix ahead of the meeting which clearly shows items relevant to you.
 

Spatial Sketches

Prior to the design meeting the above consultants listed in green are required to submit initial markups and spatials by COB Friday 20th October 2023 based on the following plans issued for initial coordination https://mxdesigns-my.sharepoint.com/:f:/g/personal/maxine_mxdesigns_com_au/EpI7e3xKH31GuOSYSvtjtscBqq40T6QiDcpM0_vln00VAw?e=9iWGb1
 

Document Management

You have all been invited to Procore for this project.
    Drawings tool to be used for drawings
    Specifications tool to be used for all Consents and Reports
    Documents tool to be used for DWGs/Certificates/Declarations
If there are any further people to be added to Procore, please fill in the below and return to me.

Thank you all and we look forward to accomplishing an efficient and successful CC together.
